data.text:
Music Super Circus has released a soundtrack album for the Swedish Netflix original film A Part of You (En del av dig). The album features the movie’s original music composed by Oskar Rindborg & Wilhelm Börjesson. The soundtrack is now available to stream/download here, where you can also check out audio samples. Also listen to the composers’ first track below. A Part of You is directed by Sigge Eklund and stars Felicia Maxime, Edvin Ryding, Zara Larsson, Alva Bratt, Ida Engvoll, Nikki Hanseblad NS Mustafa Al-Mashhadani. The drama revolves around a teenager who struggles to pick up the pieces of her shattered world. The film premiered last month and is now available to stream on Netflix.
